<br>
I used it fighting some blue ant thingies on a kill task.  I had to kill an ant soldier but it was surrounded by gray ant workers.  Here's what I did:<br>
<br>
1.  Stealth close to it.<br>
2.  Hit F5.  A 3D targeting cursor will appear on the ground right at your feet.  This is where I was having problems before because at my mouse angle, I couldn't see the cursor.<br>
3.  Using the arrow keys, move the cursor to where you want it.  Leave it there a few seconds and you'll see a message saying something like &quot;Targeted ground location 12122322.233233.2122332&quot;<br>
4.  Hit your distraction button.  You're character will make a tossing motion and you get a message saying something like &quot;you toss a pebble and it makes a sound...&quot;<br>
5.  The ant then turned to face the sound and walked towards it.  I was /stuck to him so I ended up right in perfect backstab position without every having to try to stealth right in front of him.<br>
